data.description: Meticulously maintained one level, location and lifestyle! Enjoy living in the heart of the action by the Coon Rapids Senior Center and jump on HWY 10 for quick access to shops and restaurants. This home is equipped with large doorways, vaulted ceilings, private patio and open floor plan. All living on one level with very nice natural light. New appliances, washer, dryer, carpet, flooring, water heater, patio door and paint. This home is meticulously cared for and turn key ready to enjoy.
